  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study is to assess the role of battlefield acupuncture in the reduction of
      pain scores status post adult tonsillectomy. Secondary goals of this study include reduction
      in narcotic usage, decreased nausea and vomiting, and evaluating patient factors that lend an
      increased risk of worsening pain or improved response with acupuncture.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
